02/09/2009
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- A total of 20 police officers were arrested on Tuesday (September 1st) at the Tabanovce border crossing on suspicion of taking bribes. The operation came a week after 22 policemen were detained for the same reason. (Utrinski Vesnik, Vecer - 02/09/09; MIA, A1, Makfax - 01/09/09)
